name: December.
description:
I felt the coldness ripping my skin apart.
Eyes dripping sleep.
I heard someone play tunes slowly
as I said to myself,
Who plays piano this early?
Then I saw something glowing outside through the window.
A circle. Maybe its God. Maybe an Angel.
As I took my last breath,
The first drops of December snow fell on my head and eyes.
Yes!
I died on a December Morning.
